 28 April 1916 Friday Pick for guard duti for next 24 hour . Howel , Parson , Toni Jock too . 2 hrs on 6 off . sleep down in guard tent . Bob goe over for my watch at Bazaar . found shop wreck owner gone . Dave Watt come down from Light Hors line find me . Glad to see him , have a good yarn . D Waddel Ern Nobl in same regiment .
